INSERT INTO `cms_html_module` VALUES ('15630763540538273', 'NEWS_DETAIL', 'news_list_14_1', 'news_list_14', '', '', '', '', '\r\n                <p>It is well known that water is a very precious resource on the earth and water is the source of life!\r\n                    Artificial turf and other technologies have provided new ideas for solving the difficult problems of\r\n                    desert grass growing and growing trees. Artificial turf has contributed to the earth&#39;s water\r\n                    resources. This is the fact that we have to admit, and let the small series of SKYJADE Lawn give\r\n                    everyone a detailed introduction to the advantages of artificial turf compared to the nature of the\r\n                    lawn.</p>\r\n                <p><br/></p>\r\n                <p>The emergence of artificial turf has, to a certain extent, reduced the destruction of nature to human\r\n                    beings, and at least has protected a plant in the food chain of nature. The earth will also green\r\n                    the earth because of the appearance of these artificial turfs, adding some vitality to the\r\n                    atmosphere. With the improvement of human living standards, environmental protection has become an\r\n                    important indicator for each country. Due to the increasing environmental damage nowadays, human\r\n                    beings are also suffering more and more natural disasters. It is not so much that the natural\r\n                    disasters in recent years are caused by natural disasters. People in recent years have rashly\r\n                    destroyed the natural environment and have endlessly exploited the resources of nature, resulting in\r\n                    the inability of natural resources to circulate again. The situation is growing, and some animals\r\n                    and plants are already facing extinction. It is really worth reflecting on yourself in the face of\r\n                    these humans.</p>\r\n                <p>The emergence of artificial turf not only beautifies the earth but also protects the natural\r\n                    ecological environment. This is a result of the best of both worlds for humans and the earth. With\r\n                    artificial turf, there are also opportunities for experiencing expensive football in places where\r\n                    the natural turf, such as cold and hot, does not have good growing conditions in the world. The\r\n                    contribution of artificial turf to global water resources is also enormous. In areas like Africa,\r\n                    saving water resources is of great significance.</p>\r\n                <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                <p>Using groundwater through sunlight, the water evaporates to the bottom of the artificial turf and\r\n                    collects in the sand under the artificial turf and in the soil inside the reticular pouch to moisten\r\n                    the soil. This will not only provide the soil with water for tree growth but also protect the soil.\r\n                    Groundwater does not evaporate into the air. It is understood that the artificial turf used in this\r\n                    patent is made of PPE modified material that is produced through scientific processing using modern\r\n                    bionic technology. It is highly resistant to high temperatures, cold, acid and alkali,\r\n                    anti-ultraviolet radiation and antistatic. Flame retardant and other characteristics can be used\r\n                    continuously in the desert for more than 15 years, evergreen seasons. It can also be used on the\r\n                    green belts on both sides of railways and highways to promote the prevention of massive evaporation\r\n                    of groundwater in cities. It is believed that in the near future, artificial turf will completely\r\n                    control desertification. Our lives will no longer be &quot;swallowed&quot; by smog and dust storms,\r\n                    but only blue sky and green space.&nbsp;</p>\r\n                <p><br/></p>\r\n                <p>Through the research and development on the environmental protection, durability, and comfort of\r\n                    artificial grass, artificial grass products have been recognized by more and more people. Artificial\r\n                    turf has been widely used for its unique characteristics of weather resistance, maintenance economy,\r\n                    saving of water resources, no spraying of pesticides, and use throughout the day. With the\r\n                    popularity of human sports and the permitted use of football in artificial turf, artificial turf\r\n                    will continue to grow at a faster rate due to the expansion of artificial turf use. In the future,\r\n                    artificial turf will have features such as durability, softness and comfort, recyclable recycling,\r\n                    etc. The prospects for the development of the artificial grass industry will be even\r\n                    brighter.&nbsp;</p>\r\n                <p>SKYJADE is committed to the research and development of a new generation of artificial turf and is\r\n                    mainly applied to kindergartens, courtyards, villas, roofs, balconies and other venues. In the face\r\n                    of increasingly fierce market competition, many of China&#39;s artificial turf production companies\r\n                    have begun to rely on innovation to improve product quality and gain market share with brand\r\n                    advantages. Some small businesses over-pursuing price war will only make the turf industry sluggish,\r\n                    both quality and brand, take high-tech research and development, and continuous innovation is the\r\n                    future of the artificial turf industry.</p>\r\n                <p><br/>